Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.57,0:00:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請保持房間光亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.98,0:00:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並遠離電視來觀看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.81,0:00:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想弄成漆黑的，把電視關掉好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.66,0:00:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此，綾小路博士是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.80,0:00:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為忙於重建那學士院的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.77,0:00:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，在上次寄到來信中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.21,0:00:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說還需要一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.97,0:00:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.88,0:00:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得寂寞嗎?好不容易才能見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.78,0:00:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.48,0:00:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的我，是幫不到他的甚麼忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.02,0:00:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.26,0:00:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人也變得純熟了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.36,0:00:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起在家心情能作改變會比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.53,0:00:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若看到久留美姊姊和仲人的親熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.37,0:01:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便會在妒忌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.30,0:01:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是加玲加你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.10,0:01:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已完全放下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.17,0:01:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣，久留美她怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.84,0:01:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，姊姊她在神社幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.41,0:01:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可說是阻礙著仲人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.95,0:01:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.62,0:01:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見，叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.25,0:01:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.12,0:01:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛，很清秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.66,0:01:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問...   你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.46,0:01:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可來成為銀幕上的明星嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.73,0:03:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希被羅致成為女演員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，他好像十分熱心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.74,0:03:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害啊!沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.70,0:03:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厲害，竟是銀幕上的明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.14,0:03:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是那松竹梅電影公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.11,0:03:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是令人生畏的電影天地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.54,0:03:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我這麼含羞的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒此回事，沙希你一定可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，沙希成為明星後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美便是明星的姊姊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.82,0:03:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且主人你也是明星姊姊的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.23,0:03:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我也會成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.76,0:03:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明星姊姊的主人的哥哥呢  是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.07,0:03:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.04,0:03:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何不是我啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬歲...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.14,0:03:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若姊姊這樣說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.41,0:03:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我便來試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希...今天拍攝了甚麼場面?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.20,0:04:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.86,0:04:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是戀人從背後突然抱緊的場面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的感覺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為女演員實在太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是這樣的場面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對，雖然只是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.16,0:05:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但卻十分困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳已經發麻了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.53,0:06:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希一瞬間便成為了明星呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.74,0:06:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今後會變成更大的明星，絕對是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.61,0:06:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希，恭喜你連續五部戲大受歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害啊，沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.57,0:06:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是久留美值得驕傲的妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.57,0:06:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.41,0:06:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加玲加，已承認了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法呢，因為已到了此地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.98,0:06:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希     是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.68,0:06:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明星的工作是很辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然起初總是作出令人困惑的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.86,0:06:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在卻變得十分快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是沙希呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.86,0:07:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有著很好的臉呢，沙希小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.11,0:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希...所長叫你立即去!   是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.81,0:07:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荷里活?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.21,0:07:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已在計劃了一年間的行程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.25,0:07:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是順利要成為荷里活明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是夢來  厲害啊!沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.26,0:07:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的拍攝完畢後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你便要去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問在一年裡是回來不了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.90,0:07:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,取而代之便有漂亮的未來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.17,0:07:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在等待著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.64,0:07:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我努力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那人的心在何方...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.86,0:08:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎樣做才好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.36,0:08:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姿勢不太夠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.10,0:08:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加多一點感情，拜托了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.40,0:08:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天好像完畢了，快要到荷里活呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.91,0:08:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好呢，我也想跟著去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.55,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來辭退這工作好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.22,0:08:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為會見不到喜歡的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.46,0:08:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有這人在的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雙戀嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希喜歡拍戲的工作嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.50,0:08:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,餘下由沙希所得出的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.54,0:08:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想會是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.74,0:08:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要在一年裡也見不到姊姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.90,0:09:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美只是主人你的東西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.89,0:09:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希，努力啊     是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.60,0:09:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是拋棄我而到荷里活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.76,0:09:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若中途來放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會湊你一頓啊  我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.70,0:09:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希絕對能成為世界中的大明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.54,0:10:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.18,0:10:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於見不到後，可能會有點寂寞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.45,0:10:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美是沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.25,0:10:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為久留美有主人在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.59,0:10:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.23,0:10:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請慢走...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣便好了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.43,0:10:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.77,0:11:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想做甚麼?沙希  對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎可能啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.19,0:11:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦...     姊姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.46,0:11:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是留在日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為在姊姊的身旁是比較幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.81,0:11:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣便太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.31,0:11:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.72,0:11:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜，荷里活...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對沙希來說，這可能是一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.49,0:12:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給她重新來想應走的路的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.26,0:12:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人生是很深奧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.70,0:12:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是若沙希知道了事實之後...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.14,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有砂吹入眼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.71,0:12:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，所以我便跳進海中來洗眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.51,0:12:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊...   但是這樣便太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.08,0:12:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為久留美也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認為和沙希在一起是比較幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.02,0:12:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然回來是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希.成為明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天突然送來一封神秘的信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.73,0:14:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼與加玲加相遇的命運是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.59,0:14:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要!   不是這樣的事吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鋼鐵天使久留美，第26話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.03,0:14:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加玲加新的戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是個可愛少女的故事
